\nelaborate the relations of the above results with continuous fields of Hilbert\nspaces and in so doing answer a question of Dixmier and Douady (yes for\nseparable fields, no in general). We discuss the relationship of our results to\nthe theory of perturbations of C*-algebras.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Jan 2015 21:04:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Nov 2015 21:24:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-12"}
