ow-up observations are necessary to confirm their membership. The\nrates of incidence of PNe are similar, and small but non-zero, throughout the\nGCs of the Local Group.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Jan 2015 22:17:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
